{
    "@odata.context": "$metadata#TestCaseDetail",
    "testCase": "@ConsumptionInquiry\nFeature: Consumption Inquiry\n  This feature allows the user to inquire about their electricity consumption for a specific year.\n\n  Scenario: User requests consumption details for multiple years\n    Given I am logged in as \"emma\"\n    And I start a new conversation\n    When I say \"Show me my consumption for 2022\"\n    Then the following messages are expected:\n      | type | content                                                                 |\n      | text | Sure, Emma. There are two premises associated with your name. Kindly select one to view your consumption details. |\n      | data | file:features/support/data/premises.json                                 |\n    When I say \"Sunnybrook Street 7245 / 57201 Anytown\"\n    Then the following messages are expected:\n      | type | content                                                                 |\n      | text | Unfortunately, Emma, I am unable to find any consumption information for the billing period of 2022. Would you like me to check for a different year instead? |\n    When I say \"2024\"\n    Then the following messages are expected:\n      | type | content                                                                 |\n      | text | Certainly, Emma. Here are the consumption details for the electricity service located at Sunnybrook Street, Anytown, for the period of 2024. Should you need further assistance, feel free to let me know. |\n      | data | file:features/support/data/consumption2024.json                          |\n    When I say \"then the year before that\"\n    Then the following messages are expected:\n      | type | content                                                                 |\n      | text | Unfortunately, I could not locate any consumption information for the billing period: 2023. Would you like me to check for a different year, Emma? |\n    When I say \"2025\"\n    Then the following messages are expected:\n      | type | content                                                                 |\n      | text | Certainly, Emma, here are the consumption details for electricity service at Sunnybrook Street 7245 in Anytown for the period 2025. Please let me know if you need any further assistance. |\n      | data | file:features/support/data/consumption2025.json                          |\n",
